# Typecheck before finishing

Before marking implementation work complete in `app-quasar`, run:

```bash
npm run typecheck
```

This runs `vue-tsc --noEmit -p tsconfig.json` and catches errors in both `.ts` and `.vue` files.

If typecheck fails, fix all reported errors and run it again until it passes. Do not rely on ESLint alone — vue-tsc catches template and cross-file type issues ESLint may miss.
